	   <tr><td colspan=2>hi. nenye of vallon, 26 'aquirer' here, an i just have one thing to say. for all of you out there who say rogues cant tank, yer HIGHLY mistaken. <br><br>i used to succomb to this misinterpretation, but upon getting in a great group, i changed my mind. the place: kunark, sarnak fort, back door, in the big room at the end of the first hall. the group consisted of me (26 rogue), 26 chanter, 25 druid, 25 druid, 25 ranger, 25 wizard. the settup. me an ranger were front line, chanter an druids were crowd control/buffers, with the druids healing on occaison. the wizard an chanter stayed as far from battle as possible, with one of the druids occaisonally jumpin in for a min or so to melee. <br><br>as for the mobs, it wuz horrendous. we grouped for 5 hrs gametime in that room, with only 2 deaths an 2 med times. the mobs jus would not stop spawnin on us. i think the fewest amount of mobs we had at a time wuz 4, sometimes 5 an once 6. <br><br>buffs: dont know bout everyone else, with the exception of all the casters having breeze/clarity, i had only 4 buffs. strength, sow, skin, and alacrity. with all that, i wuz doing at least 100 dmg per round, an when i could bs, i would evade then bs, mostly round 60-70, with some 80 + an a few 100+. <br><br>combat: me an ranger would melee one to death while the chanter an druids kept the others mezzed/snared, an the wizzie would nuke. i wuz the main tank (due to the dmg i wuz giving). we hardly ever stopped killing, jus kill one, move on to the next. <br><br>overall deaths: only 2. one of the druids (dont know why he died), and me. all the casters were oom, an had 2 mobs an everyone below 1/2 life. they all ran, an seein as some of the sarnaks run faster than sow, i decided to sacrifice myself to give the rest a good head start. <br><br>total exp: in 5 hrs, with 1 death, i made 5 bubs of exp. got 2 handmade woven pants ac 8 sv fire 10, (i got one, an traded em to the wizard), blade of passage (wizard won, i traded for the pants, NICE deal for me. heh). an some other nice item i won. dont know the name off hand. <br><br>so as for all you who say rogues cant tank, you ARE wrong, you jus havent gotten in the right group )<br><br>hope this helps all you mid high 20s rogues in the future for a great exp spot an group opportunites.<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
