	   <tr><td colspan=2>&nbsp;&nbsp;   Im more of an independent player myself, and gotten through levels with high difficulty, mostly on my own.  I naturally prefer soloing and doing my own things - but some things are better done with the synergy of two.  Im sure you could continue to solo even at a high level, but would require very powerful armaments and skills, and im thinking of lots and lots of patience, lol.  I can say it would go with everyone that their effectiveness becomes way higher when doubled with another - that would go with any class.  The only classes i think could only effectively solo are casters with magic which influences/manipulates the mob.  If you cant control the situation, you run the risk of dying without any support around you.  Id say thats cut and dry for any class.  Im sure I would need a group if i wanted to level effectively at an advanced level.<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
