	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well, I don't know if it's been posted yet or not (Probably) but I found a GREAT way to raise safe fall the FASTEST ever!!! I pass it alomg to any rogue I see. Here are the simple steps:<br>1)Find yourself a nice steep wall, like a zone wall, or something like that. It doesn't have to be too steep, in fact, it doesn't even have to do dmg!<br><br>2)Run up it backwards.<br><br>3)Run down!!! (Duh)<br><br>4)Repeat steps 2 & 3<br><br>What this will do is make you fall a bunch of times, and usually won't take much dmg! If you take dmg it will be low (Really depending on your skill)<br>So, no more jumping off platforms in your local tree town! Just go to the nearest zone, or a nice, peaceful wall!<br>Use this skill wisely...<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
